主要死因。农村的自然条件比城市复杂，加上安全意识不足，农村孩子的溺水死亡率是城市孩子的两倍，男孩又比女孩更容易溺水。 每年暑假都是儿童溺水死亡高发期，今年暑假还没有开始，却已经传来如此噩耗。 加强儿童安全教育刻不容缓，学校和家长该如何教育孩子避免此类悲剧重演？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7ec81c85b5b568586fc0f9ef37f73307_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/460922649"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IyKqApqad76MeEAMaCDY0NzA2ODk5IIaRpoUGMAI4aEAtcgk0NjA5MjI2NDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1622236608.478913", "card_id": "Q_328725210", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "香港一年制硕士如何，值得申请吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-627c30c7c440a665950b80f3d9c71a5c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/328725210"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyKqApqad76MeEAMaCDM1MzI2NzcwIIDk+OcFMAE4/wFALnIJMzI4NzI1MjEweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1622236608.4792042", "card_id": "Q_454325478", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 383}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有什么给大学生（大一）的建议？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "说闲吧还真不闲，学生会艺术团忙的屁颠屁颠的，但是总是感觉空。现在对未来就业之类梦想之类没大有目标吧，也很想利用大学提升自己，也想自己学会搞钱实现能自己赚点零花钱。 总之迷茫。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2d8f081eb5bb3766cda2a78f2d51a092_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "53 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/454325478"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IyKqApqad76MeEAMaCDYzMjQwODA4IMvg0YMGMAE4/QNAL3IJNDU0MzI1NDc4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1622236608.4796224", "card_id": "Q_446875392", "feed_